|--------------|---------|-------------------|------------------|----------------|
| **Relative** | `"cmd_vel"` | ✅ | ❌ | `/robot1/cmd_vel` |
| **Absolute** | `"/cmd_vel"` | ❌ | ❌ | `/cmd_vel` |
| **Node-relative** | `"~/cmd_vel"` | ✅ | ✅ | `/robot1/controller/cmd_vel` |

